# Mizizi project rules

- Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/phase-status.md` before large changes.
- Full PRD: `docs/product-spec.md`. Phased roadmap: `.lovable/plan.md`.
- TanStack Start routes only in `src/routes/` — see `src/routes/README.md`.
- Design tokens live in `src/styles.css`; reskin shadcn, avoid generic SaaS purple/indigo.
- Mock data in `src/lib/mock/` with TypeScript types; no backend until requested.
- UI quality: editorial typography, restrained motion, infrastructure-grade — not template dashboards.
- Preserve Lovable git safety rules in `AGENTS.md` (no force push, no rewriting pushed history).
